### US227 — Fuel Efficiency Metrics per Aircraft and per Route (ATCC)

### 1. Login as ATCC
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "atcc@airline.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("token", response.body.token);
%}

###

### 2. Get fuel efficiency per aircraft (L/km — lower is better)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hangar/analytics/fuel-efficiency/aircraft
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Get estimated fuel efficiency per route (based on actual flights)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hangar/analytics/fuel-efficiency/routes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
